overnment Job? As per the initial guidelines, this job is not permanent as the govt. will enroll rural women to perform banking services for 6 months on salary basis. It is a contractual type of job. However, it may be possible that after 6 months, UP govt. may select the women for permanent job.5) How many Jobs would be provided? The total number of jobs to be provided in the UP Banking Correspondent Yojana are 58,000. For this purpose, CM has already issued revolving fund of Rs. 218.49 crore to benefit 35,938 SHGs.6) What is the official Launch Date & Who Launched It? This scheme is announced by CM Yogi Adityanath on 22 May 2020 and the scheme initial source is government of UP official twitter account.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: CM Office, GoUP Twitter Account  at  "}